      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I&#39;m curious does author of the question(or even answer) checked the number of queries that spawns by accepted solution. From the question: &quot;Firing queries for each id may not be optimal.&quot;. Accepted code will do query per entity. So if inventoryIdList.size == 100 this code will do 100 selects with possible joins and stuff."
