      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "This won&#39;t work if the ids size is over 1000 or certain size depending on the DB. How about this?    <b>List&lt;Inventory&gt; findByIdIn(List&lt;Long&gt; ids, Pageable pageable);</b>"
